## Anthropic API

| Category | Package | Purpose | Equivalent In |
|---|---|---|---|
| API Client | `github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-go` | Official Claude API — streaming via `Messages.NewStreaming()`, `Accumulate()` helper, retry, auth | TS: @anthropic-ai/sdk, Rust: reqwest + custom, Python: anthropic SDK |

