## Terminal UI (Charm Ecosystem)

| Category | Package | Stars | Purpose | Equivalent In |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| TUI Framework | `charmbracelet/bubbletea` (v2) | 41k | Elm-architecture TUI — interactive REPL, spinners, viewports | TS: React + Ink, Rust: ratatui + crossterm, Python: textual |
| Styling | `charmbracelet/lipgloss` (v2) | 11k | CSS-like terminal styles — colors, padding, borders, alignment | TS: chalk, Rust: crossterm styles, Python: rich |
| Components | `charmbracelet/bubbles` | 8k | Pre-built widgets — spinner, progress, textinput, viewport, list, table | TS: ora + ink components, Rust: indicatif, Python: rich components |
| Markdown | `charmbracelet/glamour` (v2) | 3.4k | Stylesheet-based markdown rendering in terminal | TS: marked-terminal, Rust: pulldown-cmark, Python: rich.markdown |
| Prompts | `charmbracelet/huh` | — | Interactive forms — select, confirm, text input, multiselect | TS: inquirer, Rust: dialoguer, Python: prompt_toolkit |

