|---|---|---|---|---|
| Highlighter | `github.com/alecthomas/chroma` (v2) | 4.9k | Pygments-based syntax highlighting — 8/256/true-color terminal output, used internally by glamour | TS: Shiki (57 langs), Rust: syntect (base16-ocean.dark), Python: pygments |

