## Readline / User Input

| Category | Package | Stars | Purpose | Equivalent In |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Readline | `github.com/chzyer/readline` | 2.3k | GNU readline-compatible — history, completion, vi/emacs modes, multiline, password mask | TS: readline (node), Rust: rustyline, Python: prompt_toolkit |
| Alt Readline | `github.com/reeflective/readline` | — | Modern readline — full .inputrc support, Z-Shell completion, fuzzy history, syntax highlighting | TS: readline, Rust: rustyline, Python: prompt_toolkit |
| Simple Alt | `github.com/peterh/liner` | 1k | Linenoise-inspired — basic history + tab completion | TS: readline, Rust: rustyline, Python: readline |

