## File Operations

| Category | Package | Stars | Purpose | Equivalent In |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Glob (`**`) | `github.com/bmatcuk/doublestar` (v4) | 683 | Recursive glob patterns with `**` support, `GlobWalk` for streaming | TS: fast-glob/picomatch, Rust: globset, Python: glob |
| Gitignore | `github.com/sabhiram/go-gitignore` | — | Parse `.gitignore` files, test paths against patterns, negation support | TS: N/A, Rust: ignore crate, Python: gitignore |
| Atomic Writes | `github.com/google/renameio` (v2) | — | Atomic file writes — temp file + rename, crash-safe, auto-cleanup on error | TS: N/A, Rust: N/A, Python: N/A |
| File Watching | `github.com/fsnotify/fsnotify` | 10k | Cross-platform filesystem notifications | TS: chokidar, Rust: notify, Python: watchdog |
| Diff | `github.com/sergi/go-diff` | — | Text diffing for FileEditTool — unified diff, patch generation | TS: custom, Rust: similar, Python: difflib |

