## Code Search

| Category | Package | Purpose | Equivalent In |
|---|---|---|---|
| Primary | Shell out to `rg` (ripgrep) via `os/exec` | `rg --json` for structured output — orders of magnitude faster than pure Go | TS: @vscode/ripgrep, Rust: grep-searcher/grep-regex, Python: subprocess rg |
| Fallback | `regexp` + `filepath.WalkDir` (stdlib) | Pure Go fallback when ripgrep not installed | TS: N/A, Rust: regex, Python: re |

---

