| Category | Package | Stars | Purpose | Equivalent In |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| CLI Framework | `github.com/spf13/cobra` | 43.5k | Subcommands, auto-help, shell completions (bash/zsh/fish/powershell) | TS: Commander.js, Rust: clap, Python: click/typer |
| Config | `github.com/spf13/viper` | 30k | Config from JSON/YAML/TOML/env vars/flags — integrates with Cobra | TS: cosmiconfig, Rust: config, Python: configparser |
| Alt CLI | `github.com/urfave/cli` (v3) | 22k | Lighter alternative to Cobra for simpler CLIs | TS: yargs, Rust: clap, Python: argparse |

