## Testing

| Category | Package | Stars | Purpose | Equivalent In |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Assertions | `github.com/stretchr/testify` | 26k | `assert` (continue) + `require` (fail fast) — Equal, Contains, ErrorIs, JSONEq | TS: jest expect, Rust: assert_eq!, Python: pytest assert |
| Mock Gen | `github.com/vektra/mockery` | — | Auto-generate mock implementations from interfaces | TS: sinon, Rust: mockall, Python: unittest.mock |
| Alt Mocks | `go.uber.org/mock` | — | Code-generated mocks (formerly golang/mock) — stricter than testify | TS: jest.fn(), Rust: mockall, Python: unittest.mock |
| Goroutine Leaks | `go.uber.org/goleak` | — | Detect leaked goroutines after tests — catches unclosed channels | TS: N/A, Rust: N/A, Python: N/A |

