## Installation Priority

### Phase 1-2 (Foundation + Query Loop)
```
go get github.com/google/uuid
go get golang.org/x/sync
go get github.com/bmatcuk/doublestar/v4
go get github.com/stretchr/testify
go get go.uber.org/goleak
```

### Phase 3-4 (Permissions + Tools)
```
go get github.com/google/renameio/v2
go get github.com/sabhiram/go-gitignore
go get github.com/sergi/go-diff
```

### Phase 5 (Anthropic Provider)
```
go get github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-go
```

### Phase 6 (CLI + REPL)
```
go get github.com/spf13/cobra
go get github.com/spf13/viper
go get github.com/chzyer/readline
go get github.com/charmbracelet/bubbletea/v2
go get github.com/charmbracelet/lipgloss/v2
go get github.com/charmbracelet/glamour/v2
go get github.com/charmbracelet/bubbles
go get github.com/charmbracelet/huh
go get github.com/alecthomas/chroma/v2
go get github.com/atotto/clipboard
go get github.com/fsnotify/fsnotify
```

### Future (Telemetry + Advanced)
```
go get go.opentelemetry.io/otel
go get go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace
go get github.com/smacker/go-tree-sitter
```

---

## Quick Reference: What Maps to What

```
TypeScript ink           →  Go bubbletea
TypeScript chalk         →  Go lipgloss
TypeScript shiki         →  Go chroma
TypeScript marked-terminal → Go glamour
TypeScript commander     →  Go cobra
TypeScript @anthropic-ai/sdk → Go anthropic-sdk-go
TypeScript child_process →  Go os/exec
TypeScript fast-glob     →  Go doublestar
TypeScript @vscode/ripgrep → Go exec rg --json
TypeScript jest          →  Go testify
TypeScript zod           →  Go struct tags + validator
TypeScript AbortController → Go context.Context

Rust tokio               →  Go goroutines + channels
Rust serde_json          →  Go encoding/json
Rust ratatui             →  Go bubbletea
Rust crossterm           →  Go lipgloss + x/term
Rust clap                →  Go cobra
Rust reqwest             →  Go net/http
Rust pulldown-cmark      →  Go glamour (uses goldmark)
Rust syntect             →  Go chroma
Rust futures::join_all   →  Go errgroup
Rust ignore              →  Go go-gitignore + doublestar
Rust similar             →  Go go-diff
Rust anyhow+thiserror    →  Go fmt.Errorf + custom errors

Python anthropic         →  Go anthropic-sdk-go
Python rich              →  Go lipgloss + glamour
Python prompt_toolkit    →  Go readline
Python asyncio.gather    →  Go errgroup
Python subprocess        →  Go os/exec
Python pytest            →  Go testify
```
